      <title>富国银行的纳尔逊预计到 2025 年底 10 年期债券收益率将低于 4%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-26/wells-fargo-s-nelson-sees-10-year-yield-below-4-by-end-of-2025</link>
